for them.  While you can't primary spec in 2 lines, you can still balance out enough regrowth and nurture to be very useful.  You're welcomed to click on my signature to see what my template is currently at.  At 37, my best heal heals for 506, and I rarely use that at all.  The only time I use it is in RvE and on a hero and he'd have to be pretty hurt for me to even bother with it.  Not to mention it's an aggro magnet. :(<br><br>You could also give this board <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub58.ezboard.com/bhiberniasdruids">pub58.ezboard.com/bhiberniasdruids</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> a shot to find more spec info. <p><A HREF="http://daoc.catacombs.com/cbuilder.cfm?template=9442&raceid=1&classid=25"><IMG SRC="http://arnemetia.homestead.com/files/DAoC/NyssaSignatures/NyssaScale.jpg" ALT="Click to see character stats." BORDER=0></A></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm27.showPrevMessage?topicID=282.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm27.showNextMessage?topicID=282.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=282.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.execpc.com/~msippel/thedruidsgrove/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm27.emailToFriend?topicID=282.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm27.threadControl?topicID=282.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm27.s